{"tid":371890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司機被昆蟲嚇親失控 Mini Cooper撞水龍頭翻側","createTime":"2017-08-24T03:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T03:26:28.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4fae5c5e9e588e73f688fd347257c7a8815c4f","tid":371890,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>司機被昆蟲嚇親失控 Mini Cooper撞水龍頭翻側</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170824/large/1503539523_4d09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170824%2Flarge%2F1503539523_4d09.jpg&h=e2f2592b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【10：54更新】新增影片<br />\n早上8時許，姓范（37歲）男子，駕駛新款Mini Cooper Countryman私家車，在將軍澳維景灣畔停車場駛出往觀塘方向，沿澳景路駛至不足200米，范報稱有昆蟲在車廂內飛來飛去，「嚇一嚇」扭軚失控，衝向對面線撞低消防水龍頭，繼而向左翻側，范口部受傷及頭暈，清醒送將軍澳醫院治理。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170824/57120535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170824%2F57120535&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79aS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=866efb48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170824%2F57120535&h=481f465e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170824/57120535</a>"},{"pid":"768237b89ecfa8654e02b1b3773607b6930d8b16","tid":371890,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"男人老狗驚昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986b746249a062cc33e92a3ae105f2d5f6fa9c1a","tid":371890,"uid":13492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>司機被昆蟲嚇親失控 Mini Cooper撞水龍頭翻側</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170824/large/1503539523_4d09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih